`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
`computeStaminaRegenMult` acts as a **decision seam** — the game loop calls it once per tick to get the effective regen multiplier, then passes that into `regenStamina()`. This keeps the hunger-stamina interaction in one pure function rather than scattered `if (hunger === 0)` guards across call sites. The `isWellFed` reuse avoids duplicating the `> 80` threshold.
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`
